    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台本地生活/旅游出行/到家服务/二手回收类目资质标准》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1237366448834351104",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;尊敬的商家/供应商朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;您好，为适应业务发展需求，将针对《京东开放平台本地生活/旅游出行/到家服务/二手回收类目资质标准》进行调整。现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年5月8日- 2025年5月14日，规则预计于 2025年5月15日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;核心调整点：①将&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; display: inline;\">酒店预定&rdquo;调整为&ldquo;酒店预订&rdquo;；②增加国内酒店三级类目行业资质要求。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;修订具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 130.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" rowspan=\"12\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酒店<span style=\"background: yellow;\">预订</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">热销酒店</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酒店集团：（1）提供完整的公司资质，无需提交类目资质；（2）开通酒店套餐类目需提交食品经营许可证。<br /><br />2.&nbsp;单体酒店：（1）《卫生许可证 》；（2）《特种行业许可证》；（3）开通酒店套餐类目需提交食品经营许可证。酒店网络平台服务商：平台下至少有3家合作酒店。<br /><br />3.&nbsp;旅行社：（1）总社：《旅行社经营许可证》；《旅行社责任险保险单》；（2） 分社：《分社备案登记证明》、（保险若为总社统一购买请提供总社的）、总社的《旅行社业务经营许可证》。<br /><br />4. 酒店代理商：需提交资质担保书或与酒店合作协议。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.84%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"22%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 130.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"261\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.6pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 15.6pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"31\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.6pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 15.6pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"31\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.6pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 15.6pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"31\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.6pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 15.6pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"31\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酒店预售</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"22%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 14.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"29\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 72.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">国内酒店</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b; background: yellow;\">国内酒店提供行业资质二选一：<br />1.特种行业许可证 规格要求：原件照片图片清晰，复印件要求加盖酒店公章（公章要求与特行证酒店名称一致）。<br />2.酒店门头照 规格要求：酒店必须有明显的门头招牌，照片要求白天自然光下拍摄清晰的明显的门头招牌。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" width=\"22%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">营业执照经营范围需有：住宿服务相关内容。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 72.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"145\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">国际酒店</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.84%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"22%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 14.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"29\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酒店套餐</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 14.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"29\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">特色客栈</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">租赁合同或房产证明（复印件加盖公章）。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 14.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"29\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 9.58%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"9%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酒店会议</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"58%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">特种行业许可证。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 14.5pt; border: none;\" width=\"0\" height=\"29\">